<p><strong>41. 73% of consumers globally trust content created by generative AI.</strong> (Source: <a href="https://www.capgemini.com/news/press-releases/73-of-consumers-globally-say-they-trust-content-created-by-generative-ai/">Capgemini</a>, 2024)</p>
